se against an invasion from outer space. READ MORE: Japan unveils Izumo, its largest warship since World War II."], "result": {"text": "54####In response to a query from former wrestler-turned-lawmaker Antonio Inoki, Japanese Defense Minister Gen Nakatani revealed that the country's Air Self Defense Force had never encountered an extraterrestrial unidentified flying object. Inoki has pursued a variety of activities, including attempting \"basketball diplomacy\" in North Korea and claiming to have seen a UFO. In 2007, Japan discussed the legal implications of a possible invasion from outer space."}}
