ntually ran out of ammunition and only one of their number survived,. Eighteen MILF fighters were killed and a number of BIFF fighters may also died. The clash shattered a three-year ceasefire with the MILF, authorities said. A national day of mourning was declared as the men were laid to rest. Bowdich expressed the FBI's \"sincere condolences to the brave officers of the Special Action Force who lost their lives while attempting to apprehend this dangerous fugitive.\" While an SAF superintendent said at a eulogy for the fallen commandos that their sacrifice had been worth it, controversy has dogg"], "result": {"text": "55####The FBI has confirmed that Marwan, a Malaysian bomb maker and member of terror group Jemaah Islamiyah, was killed in a raid in the Philippines in January. The raid resulted in the deaths of 44 police officers and 18 MILF fighters. The attempted capture of Marwan had become a priority for the Philippines authorities and their US allies, threatening the peace agreement with the MILF."}}
